zures, coma, respiratory arrest, and death.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised when vasopressin or desmopressin is used in combination with drugs that can cause fluid retention or SIADH.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/175390/', '', 'Temozolomide, Thiotepa, Carmustine, Busulfan, Streptozocin, Chlorambucil, Lomustine, Dacarbazine, Mechlorethamine, Bendamustine, Melphalan, More', '', 1767369485);
